<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>{{title}}</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
      font-size: 12pt;
      line-height: 1.6;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 40px;
      color: #333;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #333;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 18pt;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 14pt;
      color: #666;
    }
    .reference {
      font-size: 10pt;
      color: #666;
      margin-top: 5px;
    }
    .section {
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 12pt;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .party-info {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 15px;
      border-left: 4px solid #333;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .deliverable-item {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      padding-left: 20px;
      border-left: 2px solid #eee;
    }
    .milestone-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
    .milestone-table th,
    .milestone-table td {
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .milestone-table th {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .cost-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
    .cost-table th,
    .cost-table td {
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .cost-table th {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .cost-table tfoot td {
      font-weight: bold;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }
    .highlight-box {
      background-color: #e8f4f8;
      border: 1px solid #b8d4e3;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
    .signature-block {
      margin-top: 60px;
      page-break-inside: avoid;
    }
    .signature-line {
      border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
      width: 280px;
      height: 40px;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .date-line {
      font-size: 10pt;
      color: #666;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 10pt;
      color: #999;
      border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
      padding-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>STATEMENT OF WORK</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">SOW No: {{sowNumber}}</p>
    <p class="reference">Reference MSA: {{msaReference}}</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">Project Information</div>
    <div class="party-info">
      <strong>Project Name:</strong> {{projectName}}<br>
      <strong>SOW Effective Date:</strong> {{formatDate effectiveDate}}<br>
      <strong>Expected Completion:</strong> {{formatDate expectedCompletionDate}}<br>
      <strong>Project Manager:</strong> {{projectManagerName}}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <p>This Statement of Work ("SOW") is entered into pursuant to the Master Service Agreement dated {{formatDate msaDate}} between {{providerName}} ("Service Provider") and {{clientName}} ("Client").</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">1. Project Overview</div>
    <p>{{projectDescription}}</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">2. Scope of Work</div>
    <p>The Service Provider agrees to perform the following work:</p>
    <div class="deliverable-item">
      <strong>Phase 1: {{phase1Name}}</strong><br>
      {{phase1Description}}
    </div>
    <div class="deliverable-item">
      <strong>Phase 2: {{phase2Name}}</strong><br>
      {{phase2Description}}
    </div>
    <div class="deliverable-item">
      <strong>Phase 3: {{phase3Name}}</strong><br>
      {{phase3Description}}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">3. Deliverables</div>
    <p>The Service Provider shall provide the following deliverables:</p>
    <table class="milestone-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Deliverable</th>
          <th>Description</th>
          <th>Due Date</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {{#listItems deliverables}}
        {{/listItems}}
        <tr>
          <td>{{deliverable1Name}}</td>
          <td>{{deliverable1Description}}</td>
          <td>{{formatDate deliverable1Date}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>{{deliverable2Name}}</td>
          <td>{{deliverable2Description}}</td>
          <td>{{formatDate deliverable2Date}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>{{deliverable3Name}}</td>
          <td>{{deliverable3Description}}</td>
          <td>{{formatDate deliverable3Date}}</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">4. Milestones</div>
    <table class="milestone-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Milestone</th>
          <th>Completion Criteria</th>
          <th>Target Date</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>{{milestone1Name}}</td>
          <td>{{milestone1Criteria}}</td>
          <td>{{formatDate milestone1Date}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>{{milestone2Name}}</td>
          <td>{{milestone2Criteria}}</td>
          <td>{{formatDate milestone2Date}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>{{milestone3Name}}</td>
          <td>{{milestone3Criteria}}</td>
          <td>{{formatDate milestone3Date}}</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">5. Client Responsibilities</div>
    <p>The Client agrees to provide:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Timely access to required systems, data, and resources</li>
      <li>Designated point of contact for project communications</li>
      <li>Prompt review and feedback on deliverables</li>
      <li>Necessary approvals and sign-offs</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">6. Fees and Payment Schedule</div>
    <div class="highlight-box">
      <p><strong>Total Project Cost:</strong> {{totalProjectCost}}</p>
      <p><strong>Payment Schedule:</strong> {{paymentSchedule}}</p>
    </div>

    <table class="cost-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Item</th>
          <th>Description</th>
          <th>Amount</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>{{costItem1Name}}</td>
          <td>{{costItem1Description}}</td>
          <td>{{costItem1Amount}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>{{costItem2Name}}</td>
          <td>{{costItem2Description}}</td>
          <td>{{costItem2Amount}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>{{costItem3Name}}</td>
          <td>{{costItem3Description}}</td>
          <td>{{costItem3Amount}}</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
      <tfoot>
        <tr>
          <td colspan="2" style="text-align: right;"><strong>Total:</strong></td>
          <td><strong>{{totalProjectCost}}</strong></td>
        </tr>
      </tfoot>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">7. Change Management</div>
    <p>Any changes to the scope of work must be documented in a Change Request form and approved by both parties before implementation. Changes may affect timeline and costs as agreed upon by the parties.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">8. Acceptance Criteria</div>
    <p>Deliverables shall be considered accepted if the Client does not provide written rejection within {{acceptancePeriodDays}} business days of delivery, specifying in reasonable detail any material deficiencies.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">9. Term</div>
    <p>This SOW shall commence on {{formatDate effectiveDate}} and be completed by {{formatDate expectedCompletionDate}}, unless extended by mutual written agreement.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="signature-block">
    <p><strong>AGREED AND ACCEPTED:</strong></p>

    <table style="width: 100%; margin-top: 30px;">
      <tr>
        <td style="width: 50%; padding-right: 20px;">
          <strong>SERVICE PROVIDER:</strong><br><br>
          {{providerName}}<br><br>
          <div class="signature-line"></div>
          <p>Authorized Signature</p>
          <div class="signature-line"></div>
          <p>Print Name & Title</p>
          <p class="date-line">Date: _______________</p>
        </td>
        <td style="width: 50%; padding-left: 20px;">
          <strong>CLIENT:</strong><br><br>
          {{clientName}}<br><br>
          <div class="signature-line"></div>
          <p>Authorized Signature</p>
          <div class="signature-line"></div>
          <p>Print Name & Title</p>
          <p class="date-line">Date: _______________</p>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>Generated on {{generatedDateFormatted}} by REZ Contract Management System</p>
    <p>SOW ID: {{sowNumber}} | Contract ID: {{contractId}}</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
